{
  // * common
  "update.showReleaseNotes": false,
  // * javascript/typescript
  "javascript.preferences.importModuleSpecifier": "project-relative",
  "javascript.preferences.importModuleSpecifierEnding": "minimal",
  "javascript.preferences.quoteStyle": "single",
  "typescript.preferences.importModuleSpecifier": "non-relative",
  "typescript.suggest.paths": false,
  "typescript.tsserver.trace": "off",
  "typescript.suggest.autoImports": true,
  "diffEditor.codeLens": true,
  "typescript.implementationsCodeLens.enabled": true,
  "typescript.disableAutomaticTypeAcquisition": true,
  // * window
  "window.title": "${activeEditorShort}${separator}${rootName}",
  "window.newWindowDimensions": "inherit",
  // * workbench
  "workbench.colorTheme": "Tokyo Night Storm",
  "workbench.editor.highlightModifiedTabs": true,
  "workbench.editor.labelFormat": "short",
  "workbench.editor.tabSizing": "shrink",
  "workbench.editor.showIcons": false,
  "workbench.editor.enablePreview": false,
  "workbench.editor.tabCloseButton": "right",
  "workbench.editor.splitOnDragAndDrop": false,
  "workbench.editor.limit.enabled": true,
  "workbench.editor.limit.value": 4,
  "workbench.editor.pinnedTabSizing": "compact",
  // "workbench.editor.openPositioning": "first",
  "workbench.iconTheme": "material-icon-theme",
  "workbench.startupEditor": "none",
  // * explorer
  "explorer.autoReveal": false,
  "explorer.sortOrder": "type",
  // * editor
  "editor.rulers": [80, 120],
  "editor.cursorSmoothCaretAnimation": false,
  "editor.cursorStyle": "block",
  "editor.fontFamily": "JetBrains Mono",
  "editor.fontLigatures": false,
  "editor.fontSize": 12,
  "editor.fontWeight": "300",
  "editor.formatOnSave": true,
  "prettier.useEditorConfig": false,
  "prettier.arrowParens": "always",
  "editor.bracketPairColorization.enabled": true,
  "editor.lightbulb.enabled": false,
  "editor.lineHeight": 22,
  "editor.smoothScrolling": true,
  "editor.tabSize": 2,
  "editor.wordSeparators": "`~!@#$%^&*()-_=+[{]}\\|;:'\",.<>/?",
  "editor.wordWrapColumn": 100,
  "editor.codeLens": true,
  // "editor.cursorWidth": 20,
  "editor.cursorBlinking": "solid",

  // * editor suggestions
  "editor.snippetSuggestions": "bottom",
  "editor.suggestSelection": "recentlyUsedByPrefix",
  "editor.suggest.localityBonus": true,
  "editor.quickSuggestions": {
    "other": true,
    "comments": false,
    "strings": false
  },
  "editor.quickSuggestionsDelay": 100,
  "editor.suggest.snippetsPreventQuickSuggestions": false,
  "editor.suggest.showWords": false,
  "editor.suggest.showDeprecated": false,
  "editor.folding": false,
  "editor.lineNumbers": "off",
  "editor.autoClosingBrackets": "beforeWhitespace",
  "editor.codeLensFontFamily": "JetBrains Mono",
  "editor.colorDecorators": true,
  "editor.formatOnSaveMode": "file",
  "editor.gotoLocation.multipleImplementations": "goto",
  "editor.gotoLocation.multipleDeclarations": "goto",
  "editor.gotoLocation.multipleDefinitions": "goto",
  "editor.gotoLocation.multipleTypeDefinitions": "peek",
  "editor.hover.delay": 500,
  // * emmet
  "emmet.showSuggestionsAsSnippets": false,

  "emmet.triggerExpansionOnTab": true,
  "emmet.includeLanguages": {
    "nunjucks": "html",
    "javascript": "javascriptreact",
    "typescript": "typescriptreact"
  },

  "files.associations": {
    "*.css": "postcss"
  },
  "files.insertFinalNewline": true,
  "files.trimFinalNewlines": true,
  "files.trimTrailingWhitespace": true,

  "editor.tokenColorCustomizations": {
    "[Tokyo Night Storm]": {
      "comments": "#3070de"
    }
  },

      "statusBar.background": "#040b13",
      "statusBar.foreground": "#597293",

      "panel.background": "#0b1b2f",

      "tab.activeBackground": "#142642",

      "tab.activeForeground": "#6c7c91",
      // panel
      "panelTitle.activeBorder": "#3740b6",

      // scrollbar
      "scrollbarSlider.background": "#22344b",

      "scrollbarSlider.activeBackground": "#2e4663"
    }
  },
